012.</p>\n          <div class=\"flex gap-4\" data-kid=\"306\">\n            <a href=\"#\" class=\"w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-white/5 flex items-center justify-center hover:bg-[#1a6ef5] transition-all\" data-kid=\"307\"><i class=\"ti ti-brand-instagram text-xl\" data-kid=\"308\"></i></a>\n            <a href=\"#\" class=\"w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-white/5 flex items-center justify-center hover:bg-[#1a6ef5] transition-all\" data-kid=\"309\"><i class=\"ti ti-brand-linkedin text-xl\" data-kid=\"310\"></i></a>\n            <a href=\"#\" class=\"w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-white/5 flex items-center justify-center hover:bg-[#1a6ef5] transition-all\" data-kid=\"311\"><i class=\"ti ti-brand-youtube text-xl\" data-kid=\"312\"></i></a>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n        <div data-kid=\"313\">\n          <h4 class=\"font-bold mb-8\" data-kid=\"314\">Services</h4>\n          <ul class=\"space-y-4 text-[#8fa3c0] text-sm\" data-kid=\"315\">\n            <li data-kid=\"316\"><a href=\"#\" class=\"hover:text-[#f9b800] transition-colors\" data-kid=\"317\">Sofa Restoration</a></li>\n            <li data-kid=\"318\"><a href=\"#\" class=\"hover:text-[#f9b800] transition-colors\" data-kid=\"319\">Carpet Rejuvenation</a></li>\n            <li data-kid=\"320\"><a href=\"#\" class=\"hover:text-[#f9b800] transition-colors\" data-kid=\"321\">Vehicle Interiors</a></li>\n            <li data-kid=\"322\"><a href=\"#\" class=\"hover:text-[#f9b800] transition-colors\" data-kid=\"323\">Leather Treatment</a></li>\n          </ul>\n        </div>\n        <div data-kid=\"324\">\n          <h4 class=\"font-bold mb-8\" data-kid=\"325\">Company</h4>\n          <ul class=\"space-y-4 text-[#8fa3c0] text-sm\" data-kid=\"326\">\n            <li data-kid=\"327\"><a href=\"#\" class=\"hover:text-[#f9b800] transition-colors\" data-kid=\"328\">Our Process</a></li>\n            <li data-kid=\"329\"><a href=\"#\" class=\"hover:text-[#f9b800] transition-colors\" data-kid=\"330\">Before & After</a></li>\n            <li data-kid=\"331\"><a href=\"#\" class=\"hover:text-[#f9b800] transition-colors\" data-kid=\"332\">Team Experts</a></li>\n            <li data-kid=\"333\"><a href=\"#\" class=\"hover:text-[#f9b800] transition-colors\" data-kid=\"334\">Sustainability</a></li>\n          </ul>\n        </div>\n        <div data-kid=\"335\">\n          <h4 class=\"font-bold mb-8\" data-kid=\"336\">Legal</h4>\n          <ul class=\"space-y-4 text-[#8fa3c0] text-sm\" data-kid=\"337\">\n            <li data-kid=\"338\"><a href=\"#\" class=\"hover:text-[#f9b800] transition-colors\" data-kid=\"339\">Terms of Service</a></li>\n            <li data-kid=\"340\"><a href=\"#\" class=\"hover:text-[#f9b800] transition-colors\" data-kid=\"341\">Privacy Policy</a></li>\n            <li data-kid=\"342\"><a href=\"#\" class=\"hover:text-[#f9b800] transition-colors\" data-kid=\"343\">Safety Standards</a></li>\n            <li data-kid=\"344\"><a href=\"#\" class=\"hover:text-[#f9b800] transition-colors\" data-kid=\"345\">Cookie Settings</a></li>\n          </ul>\n        </div>\n        <div data-kid=\"346\">\n          <h4 class=\"font-bold mb-8\" data-kid=\"347\">Support</h4>\n          <ul class=\"space-y-4 text-[#8fa3c0] text-sm\" data-kid=\"348\">\n            <li data-kid=\"349\"><a href=\"#\" class=\"hover:text-[#f9b800] transition-colors\" data-kid=\"350\">Help Center</a></li>\n            <li data-kid=\"351\"><a href=\"#\" class=\"hover:text-[#f9b800] transition-colors\" data-kid=\"352\">Book Inspection</a></li>\n            <li data-kid=\"353\"><a href=\"#\" class=\"hover:text-[#f9b800] transition-colors\" data-kid=\"354\">Partner Program</a></li>\n            <li data-kid=\"355\"><a href=\"#\" class=\"hover:text-[#f9b800] transition-colors\" data-kid=\"356\">Media Kit</a></li>\n          </ul>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n\n      \n      <div class=\"pt-8 border-t border-white/5 flex flex-col md:flex-row justify-between items-center gap-4\" data-kid=\"357\">\n        <p class=\"text-[#8fa3c0] text-xs\" data-kid=\"358\">&copy; 2024 MasterClean Premium Services. All rights reserved.</p>\n        <div class=\"flex items-center gap-6 text-[#8fa3c0] text-xs\" data-kid=\"359\">\n          <span class=\"flex items-center gap-2\" data-kid=\"360\"><i class=\"ti ti-shield-check text-[#f9b800]\" data-kid=\"361\"></i> SSL Secured</span>\n          <span class=\"flex items-center gap-2\" data-kid=\"362\"><i class=\"ti ti-credit-card\" data-kid=\"363\"></i> PCI Compliant</span>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  </footer>\n</div>\n",
