m a sujeira e secam em tempo recorde.</p>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  </section>\n\n  \n  <section id=\"estimator\" class=\"py-32 bg-[var(--navy)] relative overflow-hidden\" data-kid=\"201\">\n    <div class=\"absolute -bottom-40 -left-40 w-96 h-96 bg-[var(--gold)] opacity-10 blur-[100px] rounded-full\" data-kid=\"202\"></div>\n    \n    <div class=\"max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8\" data-kid=\"203\">\n      <div class=\"grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-20 items-center\" data-kid=\"204\">\n        <div data-kid=\"205\">\n          <h2 class=\"text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-black text-white mb-8\" data-kid=\"206\">Simule seu <br data-kid=\"207\"><span class=\"text-[var(--gold)]\" data-kid=\"208\">Orçamento</span></h2>\n          <p class=\"text-blue-100/70 text-lg mb-12\" data-kid=\"209\">\n            Escolha os itens que deseja higienizar e receba uma estimativa instantânea. Sem compromisso e totalmente transparente.\n          </p>\n          \n          <div class=\"space-y-4\" data-kid=\"210\">\n            <div class=\"p-6 bg-white/5 border border-white/10 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-between hover:bg-white/10 transition-colors cursor-pointer group\" data-kid=\"211\">\n              <div class=\"flex items-center gap-4\" data-kid=\"212\">\n                <div class=\"w-12 h-12 bg-white/10 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center text-[var(--gold)] group-hover:bg-[var(--gold)] group-hover:text-[var(--navy)] transition-colors\" data-kid=\"213\">\n                  <svg class=\"w-6 h-6\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" data-kid=\"214\"><path d=\"M19 11H5m14 0a2 2 0 012 2v6a2 2 0 01-2 2H5a2 2 0 01-2-2v-6a2 2 0 012-2m14 0V9a2 2 0 00-2-2M5 11V9a2 2 0 012-2m0 0V5a2 2 0 012-2h6a2 2 0 012 2v2M7 7h10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" data-kid=\"215\"></path></svg>\n                </div>\n                <span class=\"font-bold text-white\" data-kid=\"216\">Sofá (2-3 lugares)</span>\